English.Text: The Queen takes the time to answer. You flashed "ONLY DESIRE TO HELP MAJESTY," with the Columb light, and received "FOLLOW US!" in reply. You are travelling towards Trelawney, southernmost point of the Old World, where not fifteen years previous, a great naval victory was won over La Corona by the heroic Admiral Nadasky. The Lap of Victory is there waiting for you, and the Queen receives you warmly aboard. You are finally able to ask why it is she has run away.
